main event: A civilian reported seeing what he believed was a UFO over Doylestown, Pennsylvania on November 5, 1966.
interesting points: The object was lighted and larger than typical UFO pictures,The object moved slowly across the sky before vanishing to the south,No airplanes were sighted at the time of the observation,The witness had an immediate reaction thinking many others would see it too,The observation took place at night with clear visibility.
sighted object: lighted moving object in the sky
witness description: a civilian who was outside with his dogs
